meanings.definition: A surname, a variant of Lowry.
meanings.english_definition: A surname, a variant of Lowry.

meanings.definition: A male given name, a variant of Laurie or Lawrence.
meanings.english_definition: A male given name, a variant of Laurie or Lawrence.

meanings.definition: A brand name of seasoned salt and other seasonings.
meanings.english_definition: A brand name of seasoned salt and other seasonings.
examples: I added some Lawry's seasoned salt to the potatoes.

etymology.value: Surname: Variant of Lowry, itself derived from Lawrence. Given name: Variant of Laurie or Lawrence. Brand name: Named after its creator, Lawry's Restaurants, Inc.
